# Build Bible V2 — Chapter 6 (API / Server Actions / Integrations)

Spec: `docs/08_BUILD_BIBLE_V2_CHAPTER_06_API.md`

## Rules

- API routes orchestrate only — auth, parse, delegate to `src/lib/**`, return standardized responses (`apiJson` / `apiError` / `apiPaginated`).
- Prefer shared list helpers (`respondWithPaginatedList`) over copy-pasted filter/sort/paginate pipelines.
- Server Actions: `requireSession` + permission/plan guards; use `resolveActionError` and shared form validators.
- Webhook signing lives in `src/lib/webhooks/signing.ts` — do not duplicate.
- Never weaken auth, RBAC, RLS, or Paddle billing behaviour.
- Never expose secrets or raw internal exception messages to clients.

## This chapter

- Do not commit, push, or deploy from Chapter 6 work.
